doc.after: Isaias Afwerki Tigrinya is the first and current President of Eritrea attaining that status after Eritrean independence from Ethiopia in 1993 Prior to that he was the leader of the Eritrean People s Liberation Front an armed movement determined to secure Eritrean independence
